text: Ðis is geðinge Eadwaldes Osheringes & Cyneðryðe, Eðelmodes lafe aldormonnes, ymbe ðet lond et Cert ðe hire Eðelmod hire hlabard salde.
Wes hit becueden Osbearte his broðar suna, gif he Cyneðryðe oferlifde, & siððan neniggra meihanda ma ðes cynnes.
Ac hia hit atuge yfter hira dege swe hit him boem rehtlicast & elmestlicast were.
Ðonne hebfað Eadwald & Cyne ðas wisan ðus fundene mid hira friandum.
Gib Eadweald leng lifige ðonne Cyneðryð, geselle et ðem londe et CertXðusenda.
Gif he gewite er ðonne hia, his barna sue hwelc sue lifes sie agefe ðet feoh ond atee sue hit soelest sie for ða hit begetan.

Nis Eðelmode enig meghond neor ðes cynnes ðanne Eadwald, his modar his broðar dohtar, mest cyn ðet he ðet lond hebbe & his beorn yfter him, & sue ateon sue him <nytlicast> ðynce for ða ðe hit mid reohte begetan.
EgoCeolnoð mid Godes gefe ercebisceop þis mid Christus rodetacne festnie & write.
